---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main class="w-9/12 xl:w-8/12">
			<h1 class="text-center mb-10 text-lg xl:text-xl">🌟 Welcome to Wonders of Ancient Egypt! 🌍</h1>
			<div class="text-sm xl:text-xl text-center">
				<p>
					Step into the world of towering pyramids, mystical gods, and timeless stories. Here at <strong>Wonders of Ancient Egypt</strong>, we uncover the secrets, marvels, and myths of one of history’s most fascinating civilizations.
				</p>
				<p>
					This site is your gateway to exploring everything from the engineering brilliance of the Great Pyramid to the rich mythology that shaped the daily lives of the ancient Egyptians. Whether you’re a history enthusiast, mythology lover, or simply curious, there’s something here for everyone!
				</p>
				<hr class="mt-10 mb-20">
				<p class="underline">Here’s what you can discover:</p>
				<ul class="text-left">
					<li class="p-2 xl:p-4"><strong>Fascinating Facts:</strong> Learn little-known secrets about ancient Egyptian life, architecture, and innovation.</li>
					<li class="p-2 xl:p-4"><strong>Mythology Uncovered:</strong> Dive into the stories of Ra, Osiris, Isis, and more.</li>
					<li class="p-2 xl:p-4"><strong>Mind-Blowing Theories:</strong> Explore intriguing ideas about the pyramids, celestial alignments, and hidden chambers.</li>
					<li class="p-2 xl:p-4"><strong>Engaging Blog Posts:</strong> Check out detailed posts delving into the culture, history, and mystery of ancient Egypt.</li>
				</ul>
				<hr class="mt-10">
				<p class="mt-10">
					We’re just getting started! Make sure to bookmark this page, follow our blog, and join us on social media for daily updates, exciting new content, and sneak peeks into upcoming features.
				</p>
				<p>
					Have a question or a topic you’d love for us to explore? <a href="mailto:contact@wondersofancientegypt.com">Contact us here</a>, or follow us on social media for more!
				</p>
				<p>
					🌟 Stay curious and enjoy your journey into the Wonders of Ancient Egypt! 🌅
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>	
</html>
